Basic Installation
==================

./configure 
su -
make install

or 

make install
to store bin file into ~/.local/bin

Perhaps you want to set environment variable CC:

    export CC=colorgcc 

and/or
    
    export CXX=colorgcc

When "gcc" is invoked, colorgcc is run instead.
